This cutting-edge technology is said to be backed by efforts from the Department of Government Efficiency, creating an unusual alliance between innovation and federal restructuring.

While the cost-saving implications for taxpayers are staggering, the ripple effects could be even greater for investors. Analysts believe this development could light a fire under the AI sector — sending a select group of stocks soaring.

According to market expert Weiss, six specific companies could benefit the most from this sudden shift. To learn more about the DOGE Blueprint and which stocks may be on the rise, click here now.
